DarkMouse::

She went back to the commcenter and found an incoming message.  She 
responded,"I hear you. I'll send the coordinants to our base. Get 
here soon, we could always use a few bad bots."  She said with a 
chuckle.  She sent the directions to get to the black fortress and 
then contacted Drillbit, "Yo, commander, we got incoming bots. You 
might want to go and greet them."
